title: Kool & The Gang - Live At The Sex Machine (1971)
description:
KOOL & THE GANG - LIVE AT THE SEX MACHINE

Granny: What's wrong with you boy???

Jones: I dunno Granny, should I eat another banana?

Granny: What? Another banana? What? Why I ought to slap you on the side of the head boy.

Jones: Please Granny, remember your blood pressure.

Granny: You ain't uploaded enough Kool & The Gang. You ain't no Jones!!!

Jones: All this smartphone facebook shit... I've had it!!! but for you Granny, I can make a special exception.
